{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Legend of Galactic Heroes: Star Wars Versi Kolosal Nan Mewah","content":"<p>Para <em>geek</em> di seluruh dunia tentu mengakui Star War dan Star Trek sebagai serial <em>space opera</em> super epik. Bayangkan petualangan di luar angkasa dengan ancaman dari penguasa angkasa dan sekelompok ras alien penghancur dunia! Keduanya memenuhi fantasi <em>sci-fi</em> para <em>geek</em>. Jika Amerika punya Star Wars dan Star Trek, maka di Jepang juga ada serial serupa bernama Legend of Galactic Heroes.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46750\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46750\" data-attachment-id=\"46750\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46750\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1.jpg\" alt=\"01 legend of galactic heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-legend-of-galactic-heroes-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46750\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Forbes</p></div></p>\n<p>Legend of Galactic Heroes awalnya adalah novel yang ditulis oleh Yoshiki Tanaka, <em>author</em> yang lebih populer lewat Arslan Senki. Konsep di balik LoGH sebenarnya cukup simpel: apa yang terjadi jika perang kolosal abad ke-19 terjadi di luar angkasa?</p>\n<p>Meskipun merupakan salah satu novel klasik yang hadir sejak tahun 80-an, Legend of Galactic Heroes memiliki popularitas yang langgeng hingga hari ini. LoGH diadaptasi menjadi <em>manga</em>, <em>anime</em>, dan pertunjukan teater. Anime LoGH sendiri dikenal sebagai salah satu <em>anime</em> terpanjang yang diproduksi: hanya rilis dalam media VHS, namun jumlah episodenya mencapai 110 sepanjang 10 tahun!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46751\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46751\" data-attachment-id=\"46751\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46751\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"02-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46751\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Funimation</p></div></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-spring-2018-baru/\">Di bulan April lalu</a>, <em>anime</em> terbaru Legend of Galactic Heroes tayang di Jepang. Dengan judul Legend of Galactic Heroes: Die Neue These, <em>anime</em> ini akan menyajikan kisah klasik LoGH dalam kemasan baru dan kekinian.</p>\n<p>Kisah kolosal ini mempertemukan dua kekuatan besar di abad ke-36. Kerajaan Galactic Empire dan negara Free Planets Alliance bertarung untuk memperebutkan supremasi di luar angkasa. Tanpa disadari kedua belah pihak, ada satu kekuatan netral di planet Fezzan yang mengendalikan peperangan untuk memenuhi agenda mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46752\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46752\" data-attachment-id=\"46752\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46752\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"03-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: OmniGeekEmpire</p></div></p>\n<p>Terdapat dua tokoh utama dalam Legend of Galactic Heroes. Pertama adalah Reinhard von Lohengramm, pemimpin pasukan dari Galactic Empire. Dibantu ajudan dan sahabat Siegfried Kircheis serta kumpulan laksamana berbakat, Reinhard yang kharismatik dan juga jenius berambisi untuk menggulingkan penguasa Galactic Empire, agar ia bisa menyatukan seluruh galaksi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46753\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46753\" data-attachment-id=\"46753\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46753\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"04-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46753\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Anime Tosho</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun, usaha Reinhard senantiasa digagalkan oleh tokoh utama kedua, Yang Wenli dari Free Planets Alliance. Laksamana berwajah santai ini awalnya ingin menjadi sejarawan, dan menjadi tentara pun awalnya agar ia bisa mendapat beasiswa. Walaupun tidak punya pendidikan militer formal, Yang memanfaatkan sejarah yang ia pelajari untuk menciptakan strategi pintar. Kejelian Yang berkali-kali menyelamatkan nyawanya dari bahaya, dan juga memenangkan perang itu sendiri.</p>\n<p>Legend of Galactic Heroes: Die Neue These adalah anime yang cocok buat kamu untuk mulai menyelami dunia LoGH. Alasannya bukan sesederhana kemasannya yang lebih baru, namun juga ada alasan lainnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46754\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46754\" data-attachment-id=\"46754\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46754\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"05-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46754\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: All Your Anime</p></div></p>\n<p>Cerita dalam Die Neue These didesain lebih <em>streamline</em>, maksudnya memaksimalkan <em>runtime</em> sepanjang 20 menit dengan berbagai plot penting. Jika membedakan Die Neue These dengan <em>anime</em> versi jadulnya, ada beberapa adegan yang dibuang, namun hal ini bukan masalah. Die Neue These hanya menampilkan adegan-adegan penting yang memajukan plot.</p>\n<p>Perang dan intrik politik jadi santapan sehari-hari dalam Legend of Galactic Heroes. Satu episode bisa dipenuhi peperangan, dan di episode selanjutnya bisa menjadi sebuah seri <em>thriller</em> politik. Ada banyak sekali karakter dalam LoGH, dan mereka semua memiliki peran besar dalam memajukan cerita.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46755\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46755\" data-attachment-id=\"46755\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46755\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"06-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46755\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Draggle</p></div></p>\n<p>Desain karakter dalam Die Neue These berbeda drastis dengan <em>anime</em> lama yang sudah punya desain familiar. Karena <em>anime</em> ini ditukangi desainer karakter dari <em>anime</em> Kuroko no Basuke, otomatis membuat berbagai karakter pria di sini berpenampilan muda, rupawan, dan memiliki imej “cowok cantik.”</p>\n<p>Walaupun dari desain karakter terasa kurang memuaskan, tapi animasi dan kualitas grafisnya patut diacungi jempol. Kapal-kapal 3DCG memiliki tingkat realisme cukup tinggi. Badannya yang besar bergerak pelan di angkasa. Setiap tembakan yang diluncurkan dan mengenai sasaran terasa berat dan kuat. Die Neue These menampilkan adegan <em>space battle</em> yang tak hanya cantik namun juga realistis dan mampu memvisualisasikan taktik yang digunakan Reinhard dan Yang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46756\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46756\" data-attachment-id=\"46756\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/legend-of-galactic-heroes-die-neue-these/attachment/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46756\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg\" alt=\"07-legend-of-galactic-heroes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-legend-of-galactic-heroes-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Fansubbing</p></div></p>\n<p>Meskipun kelihatan sebagai tontonan berat, jangan sampai fakta itu menipumu. Legend of Galactic Heroes: Die Neue These adalah pintu gerbang yang cocok buat kamu yang mulai mendalami dunia LoGH. Walaupun lebih singkat, Die Neue These memadatkannya untuk cerita-cerita utama sehingga kamu tidak akan ketinggalan plot penting.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"391f2232-0e63-5c42-9451-01a1358d8dae"}}}